{"tid":2202144,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"龍門冰室廚師遇襲案 事隔兩個月再拉一男","createTime":"2020-09-14T10:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T04:21:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9fe18ff81ce00bc084f9c41b595447878b81ba","tid":2202144,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"今年7月6日，龍門冰室一名42歲姓黃廚師返回尖沙嘴分店開舖時，遭3名男子手持玻璃樽伏襲，導致頭破血流，其中兩男事發後兩日落網，涉嫌傷人。事隔兩個月，警方再就事件拘捕一男。<br />\n<br />\n警方今日（14日）表示，油尖警區重案組人員經進一步調查後，於上周四（10日）在將軍澳拘捕一名25歲姓陳本地男子，涉嫌傷人。該名被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於10月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200914/CTLNUIGLEFBVRMFQYHER7KSOTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200914%2FCTLNUIGLEFBVRMFQYHER7KSOTE%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=5de9536f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200914%2FCTLNUIGLEFBVRMFQYHER7KSOTE%2F&h=dc827be0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200914/CTLNUIGLEFBVRMFQYHER7KSOTE/</a>"},{"pid":"b62a9337c4787bcfa031688e752522751d702980","tid":2202144,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"係唔係同渣家軍有關係？"},{"pid":"6f87f1ae0dde74257370419fca70b3f2195f4e58","tid":2202144,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b62a9337c4787bcfa031688e752522751d702980","tid":2202144,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"係唔係同渣家軍有關係？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmmauWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmmauWQ.jpg&h=1d62079a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}